The final monster awaiting at the top of the tower was the
"Fortress Iron Giant."

True to its name as a fortress, it's large and has an
ironclad defense, suggesting that the battle to defeat it
will be a prolonged one, more so than ever before.

\C[2]There are no events after defeat in the final boss
battle.\C[17] Aim to gain \C[0]5 million G\C[17] and
challenge it with all your might!
